@endnode
@node "BangerMonitorID" "BangerMonitorID"
@next "Copyright"
@prev "BangerMenuDisk"
@{b}Get the IDNo. for the solution@{ub}

@{b}BangerMonitorID@{ub} get the number of the solution.
The number use @{b}BangerMenu@{ub}, if you want a other solution as NTSC or PAL
(z.B. CyberVision 800*600).

@{b}BangerMonitorID@{ub} start without any parameter. Chose the solution.
Note the number. Ready.

@{b}BangerMonitorID@{ub} copyright by Andre` Trettin and is a part of @{b}BangerMenu@{ub} paket.
@endnode
